business location > dx location > aws region

business location: your office
DX location: location to where you will you connect your cable, to a port this port will be allocated by AWS
AWS region: dx location will connect with aws region

dx location is not owned by AWS its a private DC where AWS has space allocated, in that you space when you request a direct connection a port is allocated for you

if you also have some space in dx location you will connect aws dx router with your router in dx location else
dx port of aws will be connected to communication partners dx port, and this  will extend port into your business locations


you will have a physical connection cable connected to a port in dx location 
dx location is connected to aws region
you will be charged for port and outbound data charges
provides high speed and low latency 
